text: James Brown Plays New Breed (The Boo-Ga-Loo) is the twelfth studio album by American musician James Brown. The album was released in March 1966, by Smash Records. ==Track listing== All tracks composed by James Brown and Nat Jones, except where indicated. ==References== Category:1966 albums Category:James Brown albums Category:Albums produced by James Brown Category:Smash Records albums
title: James Brown Plays New Breed (The Boo-Ga-Loo)
